    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You build up energy inside of your Innocence (Cross) and then throw it at any enemy within range. Make 2 ranged taijutsu attacks against any creatures in range dealing your weapons damage +1d8.<br />At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the number of attacks by +1. If this jutsu is cast at C-Rank the damage from it now instantly kills any minions classified as Aberrations, Celestials, Demons, Otsutsuki or Monstrosities and if this jutsu is cast at A-Rank the bonus damage becomes +2d6.</p>",
